race.comment: SHOW ME THE STARS (14) was a long way back last start but hit the line well to finish fifth, beaten 1.5 lengths, over 1400m at Sunshine Coast. Can easily finish right over the top of these. CHANCE WITH WOLVES (12) continued the encouraging form and wasn't far away last time when second over 1650m at Doomben. Has a good gate and gets his chance to break through. CHEERFUL CAT (9) finished seventh over 1800m at Sunshine Coast at his most recent appearance on December 14. Has found a suitable race to return and is worth including. GOT YOURSELF A GUN (7) drifted well back last start then wound up strongly to finish fourth, beaten 2 lengths, over 1550m at Murwillumbah. Can feature in the finish.
